# 🇮🇳 Welcome to India Highlight

**India Highlight** is your trusted travel companion to explore famous landmarks, offbeat getaways, and cultural heritage across India.  
We offer clean, verified, and easy-to-understand travel guides — whether you're discovering Delhi or planning a peaceful escape to Himachal.

🔗 **Visit our website**: [IndiaHighlight.com](https://www.indiahighlight.com)

